strings.Value: "Trobold fell. You don't belong here anymore."
[Attack] "I cleaned this place out once — I'll just clean it again!"
"I didn't expect to see your ugly mugs again!"

"Kobold is afraid. Says over and over times have changed, that I am dead and have to stay dead. It is all right — Hargulka will return the courage borba took from Tartuk. Or strike him dead. No matter. Trobold will stand under Hargulka."

"Ssstupid troll. Refusesss to obey. Babblesss about a new friend, a new home. I will enssssure Hargulka returnsss to become what he isss sssuposssed to be — ssservant of Tartuk, the one true massster of Trobold!"
"This our home, borba. Home of kobold and troll. You are what does not belong — you and your tribe."
"Troll will live forever. Hargulka does not fear you, borba. Borba is food for Trobold's children, not enemy."
"You think thisss will ssstop me? I am the ssspirit of revenge! I will avenge fallen Trobold. You were my deathhh — thisss time, I will be yoursss!"
"No more wordsss — I will sssquish thisss bug and ressstore Trobold!"
